    "The file header containing the image dimensions with all coordinates, the depth of pixel, the spatial resolution and the photometric interpretation are contained in this data, which is known as metadata, which is normally put at the start of the document as a preamble [355,356].",
    "According to the characteristics of medical datasets, metadata play a larger significance in this situation.",
